Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:39.03,main,Miyako,0,0,0,,Noa-chan, em đã làm gì vậy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:41.42,main,Hinata,0,0,0,,Mya-nee!
